# Comprehensive 6-Table Production Database Schema

To keep the database concise while retaining all the critical functionality (variants, inventory, order amounts) from the expanded 11-table schema, I have flattened the necessary columns into the main 6 tables. For example, `Products` now directly tracks its `size`, `color`, and `image_url` instead of needing separate join tables, and `Orders` directly tracks the `advance_amount`.

---

